Writing is your thing.&nbsp; With a pen (or keyboard) in hand, there is nothing you can&rsquo;t accomplish.&nbsp; You&rsquo;re always looking for challenges and opportunities to be creative.&nbsp; No matter how complex and mundane the topic, you strive to be interesting, conversational, clever and above all else, SIMPLE.&nbsp; From a Gen Y to Baby Boomer audience, you know how to make the material relatable.&nbsp; That&rsquo;s just what you do, and we&rsquo;d love for you to do it here. We&rsquo;re a dynamic start-up that helps leading corporations communicate more effectively with their employees.</p>
