<li>
Ability to write in various styles &ndash; from playful and clever, to stuffy and corporate</li>
<li>
Ability to write in various forms &ndash; from short and sweet, to lengthier prose</li>
<li>
Ability to research, understand, and convey topics clearly and concisely</li>
<li>
